videos.description: On the first snap of the game, Western Michigan picks off the Logan Woodside pass and its Asantay Brown going 21 yards for the pick-six.
videos.headline: First snap turns into pick-six for WMU

videos.description: Logan Woodside pass complete to Michael Roberts for 9 yds for a TD. Play stands after long review.
videos.headline: Toledo ties it on pitch to Roberts

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin run for 14-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Jarvion Franklin fights through the crowd and takes it to the house

videos.description: Zach Terrell pass complete to Donnie Ernsberger for 16-yards to the WMich 44 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: WMU FB Donnie Ernsberger hurdles defender

videos.description: Kareem Hunt run for 27-yards to the Toled 37 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Hunt shrugs off multiple Bronco defenders on nice run

videos.description: Kareem Hunt run for 38-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Kareem Hunt dances through the Broncos D on spectacular TD run

videos.description: Western Michigan's Corey Davis makes a seven-yard catch that puts him at 5,007 total for his career setting a new FBS record in the process.
videos.headline: Davis sets FBS record for career-receiving yards

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin run for 3-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Franklin powers through the middle for his second score

videos.description: Zach Terrell pass complete to Corey Davis for 1-yard for a TD (Butch Hampton KICK) Call of TD confirmed following review.
videos.headline: Corey Davis Makes Terrific Tip-Toe TD Catch.

videos.description: Jamauri Bogan breaks free down the sideline and scores from 27 yards out to put Western Michigan up 38-14 on Toledo.
videos.headline: Western Michigan running away with 27-yard TD

videos.description: Logan Woodside sacked by Keion Adams for a loss of 10-yards to the Toled 9 Logan Woodside fumbled, recovered by WMich Nathan Braster , return for 0 yards , return for 6-yards to the Toled 9
videos.headline: WMU recovers after Keion Adams sack & strip

videos.description: Zach Terrell pass complete to Carrington Thompson for 9-yards for a TD. Ruling on field of TD stands after review.
videos.headline: Carrington Thompson makes spectacular sideline catch for six

videos.description: WESTRN MICHIGAN Penalty, targeting (Caleb Bailey) to the WMich 18 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: WMU LB Caleb Bailey ejected for targeting

videos.description: Logan Woodside pass complete to Michael Roberts for 3-yds for a TD
videos.headline: Rockets TE Roberts makes leaping grab for second score

videos.description: Jamauri Bogan run for 62-yards to the Toled 14 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Bogan turns on the jets for big gain

videos.description: WMU WR Justin Ferguson shows his school pride while being carted off the field following a lower body injury.
videos.headline: WMU WR Justin Ferguson "rows the boat" while being carted off field

videos.description: Logan Woodside pass complete to Michael Roberts for 21-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Woodside and Roberts connect for third score

videos.description: Jameson Vest on-side kick recovered by TOLEDO at the Toled 36
videos.headline: Toledo's onside kick attempt goes awry

videos.description: Logan Woodside pass intercepted Darius Phillips return for 33-yards to the Toled 20
videos.headline: Darius Phillips jumps the route and picks it off

videos.description: Zach Terrell pass complete to Donnie Ernsberger for 7-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Terrell floats it to Ernsberger for paydirt

videos.description: Toledo RB Terry Swanson run for 2-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Swanson take it up the middle for six

videos.description: Western Michigan coach P.J. Fleck expresses how proud he is of his team for going unbeaten in the regular season and what it means to improve from a one-win season a few years back.
videos.headline: WMU coach Fleck: 'We're very real, we're proud of that'

videos.description: Allison Williams speaks with WMU QB Zach Terrell and WR Corey Davis following the Broncos victory over Toledo
videos.headline: Western Michigan stars Zach Terrell and Corey Davis reflect on the Broncos journey from 1-11 to 12-0.

videos.description: As is his tradition, P.J. Fleck races into the locker room and dives into the waiting arms of his team.
videos.headline: P.J. Fleck makes his leap

videos.description: P.J. Fleck delivers stirring locker room speech to his team.
videos.headline: P.J. Fleck tells his squad the job's not done yet.

videos.description: Beth Mowins amd Rocky Boiman breakdown the Broncos victory over the Rockets.
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown of Western Michigan's victory over Toledo
